Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reykjavik Summit, October 1986
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydpfr
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 17 Oct 1986
President Reagan and Mikhail Gorbachev's disarmament summit in Reykjavik ends in failure after Reagan's refusal to abandon the Strategic Defence Initiative.